{
    "Mul_Relu_Add_Abs":
    {
        "Introductions":
        [
            "============================================================================",
            "DESCRIPTION: Replace Mul + Relu + Add decomposition with Abs operation",
            "============================================================================",
            "This transformation pattern searches for an Abs decomposition implemented",
            "as a Mul, two Relu operations, and an Add, then replaces it with a single Abs operation.",

            "MATHEMATICAL EQUIVALENCE:",
            "Abs(x) = Relu(x) + Relu(-x)",

            "TRANSFORMATION STEPS:",
            "1. Detect an Add node that sums the outputs of two Relu nodes",
            "2. Detect one Relu input coming from a Mul(x, -1)",
            "3. Create an Abs node using the original input",
            "4. Remove the Mul, the two Relu nodes, the Add node, and the scalar initializer",

            "BENEFITS:",
            "- Simplifies the graph by restoring the original Abs operation",
            "- Reduces node count and improves readability",
            "- Avoids unnecessary decomposition when Abs is supported",

            "PRECONDITIONS:",
            "- The Add node must combine Relu(x) and Relu(-x)",
            "- The negation must be generated by a Mul node with a scalar -1 initializer",

            "EXAMPLE:",
            "Input: x = [1.0, -2.0, 0.5]",
            "Decomposed computation:",
            "  Mul:        neg_x = x * -1 = [-1.0, 2.0, -0.5]",
            "  Relu(neg_x)= [0.0, 2.0, 0.0]",
            "  Relu(x):    [1.0, 0.0, 0.5]",
            "  Add:        output = [1.0, 2.0, 0.5]",
            "Restored Abs computation:",
            "  Abs(x) = [1.0, 2.0, 0.5]",

            "RESULT: Equivalent Abs node replaces the Mul + Relu + Add decomposition",
            "============================================================================"
        ],
        "SearchBy":
        {
            "nodes":
            [
                {
                    "op_type": "Add"
                },
                {
                    "var": "relu2_node",
                    "op_type": "Relu",
                    "inputs":
                    [
                        "({node.input[0]} == {relu2_node.output[0]})"
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "var": "mul_node",
                    "op_type": "Mul",
                    "inputs":
                    [
                        "((IsInitializer({mul_node.input[0]}) == True) and (IsScalar({mul_node.input[0]}) == True)) or ((IsInitializer({mul_node.input[1]}) == True) and (IsScalar({mul_node.input[1]}) == True))"
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "var": "relu1_node",
                    "op_type": "Relu",
                    "inputs":
                    [
                        "({node.input[1]} == {relu1_node.output[0]})"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        "ReplaceBy":
        {
            "graph":
            {
                "initializers":
                [
                    {
                        "name": "{mul_node.input[1]}",
                        "Action": "Remove"
                    }
                ],
                "nodes":
                [
                    {
                        "name": "Abs_replace_for_{node.name}_{node.index}",
                        "op_type": "Abs",
                        "inputs":
                        [
                            "{relu1_node.input[0]}"
                        ],
                        "outputs":
                        [
                            "{node.output[0]}"
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "{relu1_node.name}",
                        "Action": "Remove"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "{relu2_node.name}",
                        "Action": "Remove"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "{mul_node.name}",
                        "Action": "Remove"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "{node.name}",
                        "Action": "Remove"
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
    }
}
